  <!-- Four Spacefarers -->  <BraixenScenario1.label>四名太空旅行者</BraixenScenario1.label>
  <!-- Having always dreamed of exploring the vast infinity of space, the three of you ran off from your handlers and illegally boarded a trading vessel during its loading. You were fortunate enough to find unoccupied cryptosleep caskets in the cargo bay. The three of you are later prematurely awakened from cryptosleep to the sound of sirens and distant charge-gunfire - only to be escorted to the escape pods by a distressed cargo technician, surprisingly, of your species. Note: Since this species has a fiery nature, it is advised not to build structures out of wood. -->  <BraixenScenario1.description>你們一直夢想著探索廣闊無垠的太空，而你們三位也從看守者的手中逃了出來，並在貨物裝載期間偷偷登上了一艘貿易商船。幸運的是，你們在貨艙中找到了無人使用且相當隱匿的冷凍休眠艙。然而不久後，你們三位被刺耳的警報聲和從遠處傳來的能量槍火聲給驚醒——只見一名看起來相當緊張不安的貨物技術員（令人驚訝的事，對方和你們是同種族的）前來護送著你們一起到達逃生艙。\n注意：由於此種族天生有著對火燄嗜火的天性，因此不建議使用木材來建造建築結構。</BraixenScenario1.description>
  <!-- Four Spacefarers -->  <BraixenScenario1.scenario.name>四名太空旅行者</BraixenScenario1.scenario.name>
  <!-- Four colonists with moderate amount of resources. Easy start. -->  <BraixenScenario1.scenario.summary>四位殖民者，擁有中等適量的資源。此為簡單開局的劇本。</BraixenScenario1.scenario.summary>
  <!-- Having always dreamed of exploring the vast infinity of space, the three of you ran off from your handlers and illegally boarded a trading vessel during its loading. You were fortunate enough to find unoccupied cryptosleep caskets in the cargo bay. The three of you are later prematurely awakened from cryptosleep to the sound of sirens and distant charge-gunfire - only to be escorted to the escape pods by a distressed cargo technician, surprisingly, of your species. Note: Since this species has a fiery nature, it is advised not to build structures out of wood. -->  <BraixenScenario1.scenario.description>你們一直夢想著探索廣闊無垠的太空，而你們三位也從看守者的手中逃了出來，並在貨物裝載期間偷偷登上了一艘貿易商船。幸運的是，你們在貨艙中找到了無人使用且相當隱匿的冷凍休眠艙。然而不久後，你們三位被刺耳的警報聲和從遠處傳來的能量槍火聲給驚醒——只見一名看起來相當緊張不安的貨物技術員（令人驚訝的事，對方和你們是同種族的）前來護送著你們一起到達逃生艙。\n注意：由於此種族天生有著對火燄嗜火的天性，因此不建議使用木材來建造建築結構。</BraixenScenario1.scenario.description>
  <!-- Having survived the landing, you witness the trading vessel overhead slowly descending into the horizon, soon followed by an explosion. There goes the ticket to your dreams... As you empty the escape pods of any supplies, you begin planning your survival on this unknown Rimworld, the technician informing you - there will be no recovery crew. -->
  <BraixenScenario1.scenario.parts.GameStartDialog.text>經歷了如此驚險的著陸過程且降落成功後，你們目睹了貿易商船就這樣緩緩地飛向地平線墜毀，並在隨後發生爆炸了——就這樣前往夢想的門票從此消失了……而當你們清空了逃生艙中所有補給物資後，你們也開始策劃了要如何在這個充滿未知的邊緣世界裡生存，然而那名技術員卻也告訴了你們——我們將不會有任何救援隊前來救援。</BraixenScenario1.scenario.parts.GameStartDialog.text>
